title: The Fugitive S02E18 Nicest Fella You Ever Want to Meet
description:
The Fugitive
S02E 18
Nicest Fella You'd Ever Want to Meet

First aired: 1/19/1965

While traveling though a small town in Arizona, Kimble (David Janssen) is arrested by the brutal and sadistic Sheriff Joe Bob Sims, a man with high political ambitions. When Kimble witnesses Sims murder another prisoner, he becomes aware that his own life is in danger.

Guest stars: Pat Hingle (Sheriff Joe Bob Sims), Dabney Coleman (Floyd Pierce), Tom Skerritt (Neely Hollister), Dabbs Greer (Mayor Duncan), Mary Murphy (II) (Thelma Hollister)
